01:09:11.640 --> 01:09:13.243
A beast... A beast...

01:09:15.920 --> 01:09:17.410
Ooh. Oh.

01:09:18.399 --> 01:09:22.724
Yes, yes, yes.
Good hungry doggie...

01:09:23.040 --> 01:09:26.089
Weenie, weenie, weenie, weenie, weenie...

01:09:26.319 --> 01:09:29.243
Weenie, weenie, weenie, weenie, weenie...

01:09:39.600 --> 01:09:40.680
